22 to January 1, 2008;
23 (3) Thirty percent for all taxable years beginning on or after January 1, 2008."
24 SECTION 2.
25 This Act shall become effective on July 1, 2025, and shall be applicable to all taxable years
26 beginning on or after January 1, 2026.
27 SECTION 3.
28 All laws and parts of laws in conflict with this Act are repealed.
